## Centrallix syntax highlighting for nano
## file extensions
syntax "cx" "\.(cmp|app|struct|rpt)$"

## function names
color brightred "\<(runserver|runclient|runstatic|abs|ascii|avg|charindex|char_length|condition)\>" 
color brightred "\<(convert|count|dateadd|datepart|escape|eval|first|getdate|isnull|last|lower)\>"
color brightred "\<(ltrim|lztrim|max|min|quote|ralign|replicate|right|round|rtrim|substring|sum)\>"
color brightred "\<(upper|user_name|wordify)\>"

